## Proposed UI/UX Enhancements

### Priority 1: Design System Foundation

> **Goal**: Create a cohesive, modern visual identity aligned with Base/Coinbase aesthetics

#### Color Palette (Base-inspired)
```css
/* Primary Colors */
--base-blue: #0052FF;        /* Base brand blue */
--base-blue-light: #6690FF;
--base-blue-dark: #003BB2;

/* Semantic Colors */  
