## Implementation Roadmap

### Phase 1: Foundation (2-3 hours)
- [ ] Set up design tokens in `globals.css`
- [ ] Create reusable Button component with variants
- [ ] Create Card component with glass morphism effect
- [ ] Create Input components with floating labels
- [ ] Add toast notification system

### Phase 2: Core Components (2-3 hours)
- [ ] Build Stepper component
- [ ] Implement step navigation logic
- [ ] Create transaction status modal
- [ ] Add loading skeleton components

### Phase 3: Page Redesign (3-4 hours)
- [ ] Redesign main page layout
- [ ] Implement Step 1: Create Campaign form
- [ ] Implement Step 2: Deposit flow with approve/deposit
- [ ] Implement Step 3: AI content generation UI
- [ ] Implement Step 4: Release/milestone tracking

### Phase 4: Polish (1-2 hours)
- [ ] Add micro-animations and transitions
- [ ] Improve mobile responsiveness
- [ ] Add dark mode toggle (if not auto-detecting)
- [ ] Review accessibility (a11y)

