## Quick Start: Getting Started

### 1. Clone and Setup
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/myreceiptt/base-campaign-vault-agent.git
cd base-campaign-vault-agent

# Checkout UI branch
git checkout UI

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Copy environment variables
cp .env.local.example .env.local

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

### 2. Environment Variables Needed
```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
NEXT_PUBLIC_VAULT=0x316c82205681B098d6a6b6Ac1fa221074F62E2E3
```

### 3. Key Files to Modify
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/app/globals.css` | Design tokens, custom CSS |
| `src/app/page.tsx` | Main page component |
| `src/app/providers.tsx` | Web3 providers |
| `src/components/` | Create this folder for reusable components |

