## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> Before starting implementation, please confirm:
> 
> 1. **Design Direction**: Do you prefer the Base-blue themed design or a different color scheme?
> 2. **Component Library**: Should we use any existing UI library (shadcn/ui, Radix) or build from scratch with Tailwind?
> 3. **Scope for Hackathon**: Which features are must-haves vs nice-to-haves given time constraints?
> 4. **AI Integration**: Is there any existing AI/agent code in the repo, or is the "Generate Content" step purely frontend for now?

